dertaxi mulighet til \u00e5 kommentere saken. Administrerende direkt\u00f8r Hege Dahle skriver i en tekstmelding at hun ikke har anledning til \u00e5 gi en kommentar fredag."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e24de3588ad2037139a1b5f3c6bc1bfc7284e5ef50d4942280c198c113c615ba"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2014-11-28T18:31:56.235Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Taxikundene blir fl\u00e5dd, mener Forbrukerr\u00e5det."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10395630.ece/o1ots8/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Taxi02_2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e92944ea029f5a64fce872f9c2b72d29cf928dc6.jpg?59770e45"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Trondheim er dyrest i landet p\u00e5 julebordstaxi -adressa.no", "88 kroner mer", "- Uforskammet dyrt", "- Vil ha ny organisering", "- Trondheim har et godt taxitilbud"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "e92944ea029f5a64fce872f9c2b72d29cf928dc6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "taxisentral as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["pris", "drive taxi", "trondheim", "uforskammet dyrt"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["forbrukerombudet", "midtbyen", "forbrukerr\u00e5det midt-norge", "kristiansand og drammen", "tr\u00f8ndertaxi", "norgestaxi trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["stavanger", "bergen", "oslo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-pers